info.description:
### JupyterD3
Attempt to bring some nice d3 plots and libraries to Jupyter notebook.

Simple wrapper on the d3 code and input is pandas Dataframes.

D3 plots supported:
- [Parallel Coordinates](https://syntagmatic.github.io/parallel-coordinates/)
- [Time Series](http://mcaule.github.io/d3-timeseries/)
- [Time Data Availability Chart](https://github.com/flrs/visavail)
